accessibility.text: Fátima's daughter called her to ask if she could pick up her granddaughter from school.
She loves her grand-daughter very much and was very happy to get a chance to spend time with her after school
She leaves the house and heads to the metro station
Arriving at the metro station, she promptly charges her card but forgets to validate it
She uses the metro thinking she did nothing wrong and meets her granddaughter
Main Goal: Pick up her granddaughter from school
